  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9a65ba13-cc22-4543-82e7-d08bd9b7708a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9a65ba13-cc22-4543-82e7-d08bd9b7708a\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/334ae170750cec76.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"567\", \"originalHeight\" : \"567\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/334ae170750cec76.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/334ae170750cec76.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e411ed4c-e503-4539-be52-775b91b5115f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5c6003c7-5ffa-466f-8471-f9193ae79539\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f13b4ac3-01b4-4554-a9c2-ef67bd8d0939\">인구의 절반은 여성입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2fb6f56a-46c1-4469-b8d6-79186cd4d4b8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c2307150-1325-40ce-ada6-c221f5db0ff7\">초경을 시작해서 폐경이 되기까지를 &#x27;가임기(임신이 가능한 시기)&#x27;라 하고, 가임기 여성은 월경(생리, mensturation)을 하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59c574ea-6476-4614-8cbd-6f93a6722e29\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dacf1bc6-a03b-4dbd-baeb-c2dfd0638be5\">그런데, 월경(생리)를 하는  여성 중 50%이상은 월경통(생리통)을 경험하게 됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-302192d7-326b-4c4c-b3cd-e76c377e3d15\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1114d41a-0aab-4834-befe-8e131f425e9c\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a8b68657-73f7-487e-825b-1eed8df61e97\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b60dd674-8666-40c8-ae7a-4e06e7561700\">2020년 11월 20일부터 한의원에서 월경통(생리통) 치료를 위한 첩약(한약)처방할 경우 건강보험이 적용되어 본인부담이 확~ 줄어 듭니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e8c5b43-62de-4806-9801-92c6195eba14\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c9d6b355-30f8-49f2-b89d-a538d8885e71\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b0b35473-07c6-4b30-ad60-04d23736d1c3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-582112a7-f797-4e6a-a7ff-379d868b2157\">궁금한 내용은 서울 동작구 사당동, 남성역 1번출구 앞에 위치한  이수한의원(02-584-1075)으로 문의하세요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59a8c40f-1d3d-4348-9a47-a72367119b2b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" i